spec_data.Name: nodejs-agent-base
spec_data.Description:
This module provides an http.Agent generator. That is, you pass it an async
callback function, and it returns a new http.Agent instance that will invoke
the given callback function when sending outbound HTTP requests.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 01:44:58 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Turn a function into an `http.Agent` instance
